sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser as Vue Frontend
    participant Router as Vue Router Guard
    participant Store as Pinia Auth Store
    participant Axios as Axios HTTP
    participant Filter as Security Filter
    participant Controller as AuthController
    participant JWT as JWT Util
    participant DB as Database

    User->>Browser: Enter username/password
    Browser->>Store: login(username, password)
    Store->>Axios: POST /api/auth/login
    Axios->>Filter: HTTP Request
    Filter->>Controller: pass to handler
    Controller->>DB: query sys_user
    DB-->>Controller: user record
    Controller->>JWT: generateToken(user)
    JWT-->>Controller: JWT token
    Controller-->>Axios: ApiResponse(token, user info)
    Axios-->>Store: save token to localStorage
    Store-->>Router: auth state updated
    Router-->>Browser: redirect to /dashboard
    Browser-->>User: show Dashboard
